The paper deals with learning shape and appearance models for medical images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of latent variables for privacy-preserving data mining, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Finally, the paper applies the algorithm to medical image datasets, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
